  m_text: 'To start picking the lock, You need to first angle the pick to the right
    spot using either A and D or the right stick! Then, hold space or RT to test
    the position. The farther the pick moves, the closer you are to the right spot!


    Be
    careful though, hold it at the wrong angle for too long and you will need to
    start over.


    Press Q on keyboard or Y on controller to continue.'
